name: Baby2Body Limited
description: Developer of a digital ecosystem intended for women to have all their wellness needs met, from first period to last. The company connects female health consumers with wellness experts, products, and services, in a personalized way and provides women with a unique health profile based on data inputs and receive personalized wellness solutions to create a network with women and get the wellness support they need to live better and gain powerful insights in order to offer more effective solutions, enabling women to track and monitor their personal health data from optimum time to conception to postpartum recovery.

name: Nuren Group Limited
description: Developer of a community platform designed to address female family matters. The company's platform specializes in covering women's journey from getting married to entering motherhood by gathering related vendors and services under one roof, enabling users to discover inspirations, find suitable products, and shop online.

name: Neqabty Inc.
description: Developer of a mobile-based financial application designed to provide automated syndicate services. The company's application offers payment of service costs, medical services, and booking events and trips, enabling clients to pay for their medical applications such as prescriptions, renewals, and medical fees.

name: NUME LLC
description: Developer of a monthly subscription solution Platform intended to help women purchase contraceptives and access medical consultations in a simple and affordable way. The company's platform provides advice on sexual and reproductive health, and medical evaluation and offers contraceptive methods and pills at home, enabling women to eradicate unwanted pregnancies and reduce the occurrence of sexually transmitted diseases.

name: SAIB & Co. Inc.
description: Manufacturer of intimate cosmetics intended to tackle the entrenched cultural taboos around female sexuality. The company's offerings include sexual wellness products like a condom made from plant latex without unnecessary additives and artificial pigments designed from the perspective of women, enabling women to feel comfortable and proud to carry them without any shame or stigma.

name: Vivosens INC.
description: Developer of a wellness application designed for personalized nutrition and lifestyle advice based on urine sample analysis. The company's application guides users to make healthier choices by tracking parameters such as vitamin C, magnesium, calcium, salinity, oxidative stress, hydration, ketones, and protein straight to their phone in seconds based on weekly at-home urine tests, enabling users to track and know their bodies and health conditions.
